node.text: Who's ready for the next challenge?! @tammyhembrowfitness It's starting September 27 and will be available for purchase in the Tammy Fit App THIS WEEK.  I've been SOOO excited for this one.  Definitely my fave kind of challenge 😏🍑 Stay tuned for updatesss.  As for my tone & shred ladies you KILLED it 😭 I'm so damn proud wow.  Now let's keep going !! Long term results come from consistency so now isn't the time to let up !  Link in bio to download the app 💓
